  ('dietitian-moex-03238', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某縣市衛生局在執行「長期照護機構營養改善計畫」前，先蒐集各長期照護機構之供餐資料。此步驟是 屬於營養教育計畫內容之那一部分？', '["確認問題", "訂定目標", "研擬對策和執行計畫", "評價計畫成效"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aab8dcf25588", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fbd287ac8cfb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03239', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '設計社區營養計畫時，常會運用到策略行銷4P是指：', '["plan, product, price, place", "plan, promotion, price, place", "product, price, place, promotion", "product, price, place, people"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aab8dcf25588", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fbd287ac8cfb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03240', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '陳先生自覺有信心可以在宴會當中克服貪吃甜點的毛病，以達到體重控制的目的。此種能力為：', '["自我效能（self-efficacy）", "情緒喚起管理（management of emotional arousal）", "成就的自我控制（self-control of performance）", "行為能力（behavioral capability）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aab8dcf25588", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fbd287ac8cfb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03241', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '對孕婦進行營養介入，其中每100人就有25位孕婦未達標準體重；這25人中有15人接受營養諮詢；其 中需轉介的10人中有3人轉介至照顧機構。15位孕婦在接受營養諮詢後，有12人體重增加達到標準。 評估時以「15位孕婦在接受營養諮詢後，有12人體重增加達到標準」，此為何種評估？', '["過程評估（process evaluation）", "結果評估（outcome evaluation）", "經濟評估（economic evaluation）", "影響評估（impact evaluation）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aab8dcf25588", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fbd287ac8cfb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03242', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據歷年來所有的全國性營養調查結果，下列何種營養素的攝取量始終不及DRIs？', '["維生素B", "維生素E", "鈣", "鐵 6"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aab8dcf25588", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fbd287ac8cfb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
